<topic id="nvdl-schema-diagram-outline-view">
  <title>NVDL Outline View</title>
  <prolog>
    <metadata>
      <keywords><indexterm>Editing NVDL Schemas<indexterm>schema diagram<indexterm>Outline
            view</indexterm></indexterm></indexterm></keywords>
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
  <body>
    <p>The <uicontrol>Outline</uicontrol> view for NVDL schemas presents a list with the named or
      anonymous rules that appear in the diagram and it allows for quick access to a rule by name.
      By default, it is displayed on the left side of the editor. <ph
        conkeyref="reusables-editing-modes/reopen-view"/></p>
  </body>
